data.description: Welcome to the most meticulously maintained Megatel home in the neighborhood! Beautiful hardwood floors greet you and flow throughout.  The open floor plan allows the perfect hosting space!  The kitchen is home to gas cooktop, a plethora of cabinets and countertop prep space. Coffered ceilings are the highlight of the living room, along with the cozy fireplace.  The primary and secondary bedrooms are split for the perfect amount of privacy.  The oversized primary celebrates a bay window which provides tons of natural light. The primary bath offers a jetted bathtub, extended shower with seating and marble dual countertop space.  Always enjoy endless hot showers with the tankless water heater!  Moving to the backyard, you will enjoy 8’ privacy fencing and the perfect amount of space for an upcoming family football night!  This desired community has NO MUD or PID!
